pip search (*)>> for  searching about packages
pip install (*)>> installing packages
pip uninstall (*) >> for uninstalling packages
pip list >> listing installed packages
pip list -o >> for listting outdated packages
pip list -u >> for listing updated packages
pip install -u () >> for updating packages
pip freeze > file.txt  >> to write down all packages into text file 
pip install -r textFile >> to install packages form text file
